      "module_path": "adr_decision::git_blob_adapter",
      "docs": "Git-blob adapter that reads ADR markdown files from `origin/<branch>:knowledge/adr/` via `git ls-tree` (directory listing) and `git show` (blob content). The merge-gate counterpart to `FsAdrFileAdapter`: used exclusively by `merge_gate_adapter::read_adr_verify_report` so that chain ⓪ ADR signal evaluation is performed against the PR branch ref rather than the local worktree. Implements `domain::AdrFilePort` — `list_adr_paths` uses `git_ls_tree_dir` (symlinks skipped at listing stage), `read_adr_frontmatter` uses `fetch_blob_safe` (symlinks rejected fail-closed). Branch is validated by the merge-gate adapter before construction.",
